# Generated artifacts from example runs (PLY frames, intermediate meshes).
# Each example writes to its own out/ directory (e.g.
# examples/mesh/<domain>/<crate>/out/) — kept local for the visuals
# pass, never committed. `**/out/` matches at any nesting depth so the
# standardization layout's nested crates are covered. See README.md for
# the layout convention.
**/out/
